<plot>Desperate to comprehend the fleeting memories of her father's disappearance, 11 year old Madison Rye searches for the aliens she believes abducted him. In the process, she strikes up an unlikely friendship with Harry, a fifty year old trash collector who shares Madison's passion for the other-worldly, and alienation from the social world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?351211</url></doc>
